metadata.name: Cash is Dead
metadata.description:
It is the beginning of a new era for Franksy... starting by minting an open edition of my first ever painting done in 2015 called ‘Cash Is Dead’.

The original work is mixed media on canvas, donning the iconic Frank Wilder motif; created with authentic U.S. legal tender, aerosol paint and epoxy resin.

The digital recreation of this work represents the idea of exchange, culture and creativity going digital.

Each edition minted of ‘Cash is Dead’ will act as a unit of exchange, where one or more editions will be burned for in exchange for future cultural experiences and creative endeavours created by yours truly. 

Stay wild, stay free.

Frank
